snippet.title: Hollywood Actors Johnny Depp Amber Heard in Trouble AGAIN!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp, Amber Heard, Hollywood Actor Johnny Depp in Trouble AGAIN, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard dog, Apology for biosecurity breach Australia

Hollywood Actors Johnny Depp Amber Heard in Trouble AGAIN! Amber heard split and filed for divorce with actor husband Johnny depp after making Australian biosecurity apology. Having recently given a public statement on Australian Customs Laws, the couple have announced their split up today after Amber files for divorce, just 15 months after their marriage began. This is a breakdown of WHY the Australian Government has the stance it does on customs / bio-security. Johnny Depp and wife Amber Heard apologized last week for breaching Australian Federal Laws on importation of animals and failing to declare same. This is actually a very serious offence, and this video touches on WHY...Amber Heard has received a one-month good behavior bond without conviction for falsifying her arrival card. The actress and her husband both smiled when the penalty was delivered by magistrate Bernadette Callaghan. They hugged each other tightly as the court room was cleared. Ms Callaghan said she accepted Heard had made a genuine mistake. "I accept she did not set out to deliberately deceive the Australian authorities, I also accept she is not a person who thinks she is above the law," Ms Callaghan said. The actress will have to pay a $1000 fine if she does not remain of good behaviour for the next month.
